hurch - you see, Trinity - the Rector of Guildford then, I suppose as now, he controlled three churches. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1584246\charrsid11160377 Holy}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
