\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4792939\charrsid11160377  of it. Yes, I had to save half of it. Mother was very strict in that respect, she - opened a banki
ng account for every one of us and - every week you put, if its only a penny a penny went away to your savings.
