Well, their - their kindness, their symp - sympathy to those people below them and the - their employees - the - it's a bit difficult to say now just off hand that one - on the other - on the other hand you get a case where I - I
 knew one man that was a - a bricklayer, an ordinary brick layer but he was a very nice man and he kept his house and gardens in a beautiful - it was just like a little jewel - yes, and - everybody looked on him as being a gentleman, you see, because he w
as kind, sympathetic and always spoke to people in a nice and polite manner.
