\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1584246\charrsid11160377 we\rquote d}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4792939\charrsid11160377  get into trouble if we did wrong and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2559348 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4792939\charrsid11160377 Did your parents ever say, if you were naughty, I'll call a policeman?
