 and taught us to save money and look after money. You see in those days there wasn't any unemployment money, there wasn't any relief whatever and a golden sovereign was a golden sovereign. We - well, we were taught to look after our money. Take care of t
hings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2559348 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4792939\charrsid11160377 You don't remember if you ever felt anxious about this as a child?
